{"tid":1530422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警察犯法，有片]田心分區指揮官潘毅德涉犯非法禁錮罪","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:34:17.000Z","uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6c6b37277aecdc3201df4b19d5087b612047b0","tid":1530422,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:09:14.000Z","msg":"條片係蘋果新聞既。應係要訂閱左蘋果新聞至睇到以下網頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190902/20760652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F20760652&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2Fazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=92789f42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190902%2F20760652&h=d52e47b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190902/20760652</a><br />\n由3:36開始<br />\n<br />\n然後至3:47，潘毅德等於係非法拘捕，因為沙田區議員李世鴻係有言論自由大嗌「黑警暴打市民可恥」的；此舉並無犯法、亦無合理由相信此行為係有犯罪意圖。<br />\n<br />\n由於並無合理理由可以拘捕李世鴻，因此田心分區指揮官潘毅德等於係犯左非法禁錮罪。<br />\n<br />\n由於刑事案一般要由律政師提出起訴，案件才會上法庭審理。而由於律政師皆受律政師師長鄭若驊此一賤婦所管束，因此可以預見，律政師將不會起訴田心分區指揮官潘毅德。因此，沙田區議員李世鴻可以私人檢控的形式，作出刑事案件的提告(並向法庭要求一切費用由敗方承擔)。<br />\n[注意：這個訴訟是大很重要的社會意義，因為可以約束警隊，不能夠無法理依據下故亂拘捕人！]"},{"pid":"def8a8d7c2803841d3e44442a90976ae5fd7a9fd","tid":1530422,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:10.000Z","msg":"呢條死鬼佬一定要好好招呼"},{"pid":"3c2ce1afed943eb534ca88fcee3afe3b64fe07a0","tid":1530422,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"def8a8d7c2803841d3e44442a90976ae5fd7a9fd","tid":1530422,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:32:10.000Z","msg":"呢條死鬼佬一定要好好招呼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"由法庭去入罪係最好既....... 因為有社會意義，可以約束警隊，不能夠無法理依據下故亂拘捕人！"},{"pid":"af19f75aa80bcdfbbf39201222518778ba786f61","tid":1530422,"uid":218081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"push 一人一case告黑狗"},{"pid":"79d50c6e00ac6ab3a2e03dfffd4d074d85bcd2ab","tid":1530422,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"呢度有相同既法律觀點：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2Fazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=6e84e84b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E8%81%B7%E5%8B%99%E5%92%8C%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B&h=e8a2bd0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/警員執行職務和過分武力</a><br />\n<br />\n//...........又如一旦警察在無合理基礎之上進行拘捕，警員亦不會被視作在執行職務警察，並會構成非法禁錮（如在逮捕的情況），從而在法律上容許被警察非法逮捕或襲擊者使用合理武力脫身。（見：Yeung May Wan &amp; Others v HKSAR (2005) 8 HKCFAR 137, 160B-J; 朱經緯案；McBean v Parker (1983) 147 JP 205）&hellip;/"},{"pid":"555f79b587d8404d9824b2a03413997b2f538373","tid":1530422,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}